query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('conditional',
'extjs',
'ffmpeg',
'fonts',
'hadoop',
'ionic-framework',
'mongoose',
'mvvm',
'object',
'orm',
'plsql',
'pygame',
'sql-server-2005',
'webforms');
